15:26.259 --> 15:28.052
D.J., go to your room.

15:28.094 --> 15:30.555
I'm gonna talk to Jesse and then

15:28.094 --> 15:30.555
I'll come up and talk to you.

15:30.597 --> 15:32.682
This is so unfair.

15:33.933 --> 15:35.184
How could you take his side

15:35.226 --> 15:38.104
